| &nbsp;&nbsp; 1 &nbsp;&nbsp;
| &nbsp;&nbsp; R &times; (π / 2)<sup>2</sup> / 2! &nbsp;&nbsp;
|  &nbsp;&nbsp; 4241&prime; &nbsp; 09&prime;&prime; &nbsp;  00&prime;&prime;&prime;  &nbsp;&nbsp;
|  &nbsp;&nbsp; u-na-dha-na-krt-bhu-re-va &nbsp;&nbsp;
|-
| &nbsp;&nbsp;  2 &nbsp;&nbsp;
|  &nbsp;&nbsp; R &times; (π / 2)<sup>4</sup> / 4!  &nbsp;&nbsp;
|  &nbsp;&nbsp; 872&prime; &nbsp; 03&prime;&prime; &nbsp; 05 &prime;&prime;&prime;  &nbsp;&nbsp;
| &nbsp;&nbsp; mī-nā-ngo-na-ra-sim-ha &nbsp;&nbsp;
