|  &nbsp;&nbsp; 071&prime; &nbsp; 43&prime;&prime; &nbsp;  24&prime;&prime;&prime; &nbsp;&nbsp;
|  &nbsp;&nbsp; bha-drā-nga-bha-vyā-sa-na &nbsp;&nbsp;
